(84)
of the total pre-tax amount recorded in aoci, $2,587 million
related to cash flow hedges of forecasted transactions of which we expect to
transfer $1,402 million to earnings as an expense in the next 12 months
contemporaneously with the earnings effects of the related forecasted
transactions. in 2009, we recognized insignificant gains and losses related to
